    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1914-05-02T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1914-05-02T00:00:00-05:00" n="748"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d748">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00/23425.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Mediators</gloss> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Translation.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-05-02">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 2, 1914</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: With the acceptance of our good offices by all
                    the parties interested in the pacific and amicable settlement of the conflict
                    between the United States and Mexico, the time has arrived formally to begin
                    negotiations.</p>
                <p>For this purpose it is necessary that each of the parties name its
                    representatives before the Mediators for the purpose of discussing the bases of
                    settlement.</p>
                <p>After representatives have been appointed, we shall hasten to fix the date for
                    the inauguration of the conference.</p>
                <p>We renew [etc.]</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <list>
                            <item>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">D. da Gama</hi>.</item>
                            <item>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">R. S. Naón</hi>.</item>
                            <item>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Ed’o Suarez Mujica</hi>.</item>
                        </list>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
